{"TopicId":51920,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Riddles","CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-05T03:12:01Z","PageNum":67,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-15T18:10:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Mechanic\u0022 data-cite=\u0022The Mechanic\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EActually Mercury was what I had in mind. The never hurried line was more to be seen in the sense of a cyclical appearance. To be fair, it might have been a bit ill-worded.\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENot to be the only to carry the name\u003C/em\u003E. -\u0026gt; Referring to quicksilver, also known as Mercury and Mercury project.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eit has neither company nor aim\u003C/em\u003E. -\u0026gt; No moons, orbiting the Sun.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EIn olden times a deity\u0027s name it carried\u003C/em\u003E -\u0026gt; \u0022Apollo, the ancient Greek name for the planet \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercury_%28planet%29\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMercury\u003C/a\u003E, when observed just before dawn as a morning star\u0022 \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apollo_%28disambiguation%29\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E(Source)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eonly to be seen in the morning, it never hurried.\u003C/em\u003E -\u0026gt; Morning star as well as orbit\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENever to be seen passing between the dusk and the dawn.\u003C/em\u003E -\u0026gt; Not visible in the night, reference to the God Mercury guiding souls into the underworld.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWell, it could have been formulated a bit better.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYeesh. Sooo... Since I was the first to mention Mercury, is it my turn to go?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr do you want to try again?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souper","CreatedById":86003,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-15T18:12:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo... does that mean Starwhip gets to post?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Mechanic","CreatedById":119038,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-15T18:20:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI would say he gets the post. Sure the riddle was a bit ill-worded but he mentioned Mercury first.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T01:15:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll take it up, but geez, I\u0027m rusty. Can\u0027t even think of a good subject.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll have one eventually.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sun","CreatedById":66710,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T02:03:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESeeing as he can\u0027t come up with a riddle, I get to post mine:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe more you take away from me, the larger I become. What am I?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"briansun1","CreatedById":67451,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T02:23:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sun\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Sun\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESeeing as he can\u0027t come up with a riddle, I get to post mine:\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThe more you take away from me, the larger I become. What am I?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA hole/ditch in the ground?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sun","CreatedById":66710,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T02:28:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECorrect!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E10chars\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"briansun1","CreatedById":67451,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T02:37:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022